Package: flightpath
Type: Package
Title: Independent package for use with the "OpenSky Network" API
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Jalen", "Jiang", email = "jyj@uchicago.edu", role = c("cre", "aut")), 
    person("Adrian", "Przezdziecki", email = "adrianprzez99@gmail.com", role = "aut"))
Description: Track and record flights live. Use interpolation to draw paths from event coordinates. 
    Linear reference paths to populate path segments with event attributes.
